column4: Ottawa Charge Unisex Line Change Trucker Hat
column5:
Top off your look with the PWHL Ottawa Charge Unisex Line Change Trucker Hat. Featuring the team name prominently on the front, this hat combines classic style with modern comfort. The shell is made from 100% cotton, while the lining and mesh provide breathability with 100% polyester construction. Designed as a one-size-fits-most, this trucker hat is perfect for showing your team pride wherever you go.

Material Details: Shell: 100% cotton; Lining & mesh: 100% polyester.

Care Instructions: Spot clean as needed.

PWHL Ottawa Charge - Professional Women's Hockey League Official Product

column4: Toronto Sceptres Unisex Peace Collective Fleece Quarter Zip
column5:
Stay warm and stylish with the PWHL Toronto Sceptres Unisex Peace Collective Fleece Quarter Zip, a standout piece from our exclusive collaboration with Peace Collective. This quarter zip features a sleek silver zipper pull, a stand-up collar, and an embroidered design on the front chest. Made from soft and durable fabric, it’s perfect for layering on game day or any day.

Material Details: 60% cotton, 40% polyester ringspun fleece .

Care Instructions: Machine wash cold, tumble dry low or hang dry.

column4: Toronto Sceptres Unisex Peace Collective Vintage Fleece Crew
column5:
Elevate your casual wardrobe with the PWHL Toronto Sceptres Unisex Peace Collective Vintage Fleece Crew, a key piece from our exclusive collaboration with Peace Collective. Featuring an oversized screenprint on the front, this crewneck is both stylish and comfortable. It’s ribbed at the neck, waistband, and wrists for a perfect fit and preshrunk to ensure it stays that way. Crafted from cozy fleece fabric, it’s perfect for staying warm while supporting your team.

Material Details: 60% cotton, 40% polyester ringspun fleece.

Care Instructions: Machine wash cold, tumble dry low or hang to dry.

column4: PWHL Peace Collective Own the Ice Tote
column5:
Carry your PWHL pride everywhere with the Peace Collective ""Own the Ice"" Tote, a retro-inspired piece from our Peace Collective collaboration featuring all six new teams. This tote is designed for both style and functionality, with a large main compartment, reinforced shoulder straps, and a bold printed graphic that showcases your love for the game.

Material Details: 100% cotton canvas.

Care Instructions: Spot clean as needed.

PWHL - Professional Women's Hockey League Official Product

column4: PWHL Unisex Peace Collective Own the Ice Letterman Jacket
column5:
Celebrate the PWHL with the Limited Edition Peace Collective "Own the Ice" Letterman Jacket, a must-have collector's item featuring detailed embroidery and appliqué representing all six new team names and logos. This standout piece from our Peace Collective collaboration has strikingly different colored sleeves, complemented by ribbing at the collar, wrists, and waistband for a classic fit. With two side pockets, an interior pocket, and snap button closures, this jacket is as functional as it is stylish.

Material Details: 100% Organic Cotton.

Care Instructions: Dry clean recommended to maintain quality.

PWHL - Professional Women's Hockey League Official Product

column4: Boston Fleet Unisex Bauer Front Logo Back Name T-Shirt
column5:
Show your team spirit with the PWHL Boston Fleet Unisex Bauer Front Logo Back Name T-Shirt. Crafted from a soft and light 60% cotton, 40% polyester blend, this tee offers a comfortable, tapered hockey fit. Featuring a ribbed collar for added durability, the shirt showcases the PWHL team logo centered on the front, a team graphic on the back, and the PWHL logo on the wearer's right arm.

Material Details: 60% cotton, 40% polyester.

Care Instructions: Machine wash cold, tumble dry low.

PWHL Boston Fleet - Professional Women's Hockey League Official Product

The shell is made from 100% cotton, while the lining and mesh provide breathability with 100% polyester construction. Designed as a one-size-fits-most, this trucker hat is perfect for showing your team pride wherever you go.

Material Details: Shell: 100% cotton; Lining & mesh: 100% polyester.

Care Instructions: Spot clean as needed.

Perfect for making a statement, the Kasten Jacket effortlessly blends practicality with a nod to your PWHL affiliation. Embrace effortless elegance and stand out with this standout piece.  

Material Details: 100% Wool.

column4: New York Sirens Adult Royalty Quarter Zip Podium Hybrid Jacket
column5:
The New York Sirens Adult Royalty Quarter Zip Podium Hybrid Jacket is a mid-weight performance piece designed for all-day comfort and mobility. Crafted with strategically selected fabrics, this jacket ensures maximum flexibility, making it perfect for both in-the-arena action and outdoor adventures. It features high-quality 3D printed logos, front kangaroo zipper pockets, and dual-sided hood and waist pulleys for a customizable fit. The athletic design is further enhanced with thumbholes and a scalloped bottom, offering a sleek, comfortable fit that moves with you.

Material Details: 94% Polyester, 6% Spandex

Care Instructions: Machine wash cold, tumble dry low.

PWHL - Professional Women's Hockey League Official Products

column4: New York Sirens Adult Royalty Sherpa Half Zip Jacket
column5:

Made from soft, high-quality fleece, it includes a half-zip closure, a kangaroo pocket, and woven cuffs for added functionality. The silicone team patch beneath the zipper adds a touch of team pride, while the hooded neckline and jersey-lined pockets provide extra comfort and convenience.

Care Instructions: Machine wash cold, hang to dry.
